# Licensing

This repository contains two categories of content licensed separately.

## Specification Text

The specification text — including `draft-zivis-ztnp-00.md`, `README.md`,
and any accompanying prose documentation describing the protocol — is licensed
under the **Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC-BY-4.0)**.

See [LICENSE-SPEC](./LICENSE-SPEC) for the full text.

### IETF Contribution

Portions of the specification intended for IETF submission are additionally
offered under the IETF Trust Legal Provisions (TLP) applicable to IETF
contributions. Contributors agree that IETF-submitted material may be used
under BCP 78/79 and the associated IETF Trust license terms as in effect on
the date of contribution.

## Code

Reference implementations, code samples, test vectors, and any code in
directories such as `reference/`, `test-vectors/`, or `examples/` are licensed
under the **Apache License, Version 2.0**.

See [LICENSE-CODE](./LICENSE-CODE) for the full text.

## Summary

| Content | License |
|---------|---------|
| Specification text (`*.md` describing the protocol) | CC-BY-4.0 (+ IETF TLP for submitted portions) |
| Reference code, test vectors, examples | Apache-2.0 |

## Trademarks

"ZIVIS" and related product names, logos, and marks are trademarks of ZIVIS
and are not licensed under this file. Implementations and derivative works
MUST NOT imply endorsement by ZIVIS or suggest that an implementation is a
"ZIVIS-issued" Posture Assertion unless the assertion was actually issued by ZIVIS.

## Profiles

The ZTNP specification defines a Profile extension mechanism (Appendix D
of the draft). Individual profiles — whether published by ZIVIS, other
vendors, or industry consortia — are separately-licensed works and are
out of scope for this repository. The ZTNP negotiation protocol defined
by this specification is open and free to implement.
